text: Corus pseudocostiger is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1936.BioLib.cz - Corus pseudocostiger. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It feeds on Acacia plants. ==References== Category:Corus (genus) Category:Beetles described in 1936
